channel.title: Ryan's Client V3 Is ALMOST HERE!
channel.description:
Hey guys this is Ryan. I am showing my V3 which I will release this week! :eek:
Here is a few pics to get started. I AM NOT COMPLETELY DONE! I still need to add some models(like lunar [s]shit[/s] stuff)
[IMG]http://i296.photobucket.com/albums/mm187/RyanR0x/evolved0006-1.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i296.photobucket.com/albums/mm187/RyanR0x/evolved0005.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i296.photobucket.com/albums/mm187/RyanR0x/evolved0004-1.png[/img]
It Includes the same stuff as V2 plus a new models and ALL the skill icons. Plus as you can see i had a little fun with the inventory box and the chat box. I am tired of the same stuff like brown and dragons, so i made it wood and paper :P
It still has music! Please tell me what you think about the client! (V2 and the soon coming V3!)
